snippet.title: Eddie Bauer
snippet.description:
Our founder, Eddie Bauer, was an outdoor guide.  He dedicated his life to making gear that got people outside.  100 years later, we're still sharing what Eddie taught us by working side-by-side with guides to build technical gear designed to fit today's adventures.  Because just like Eddie, we believe that life is better outside--where it's wild, beautiful and mean to be shared.  

Eddie Bauer is an outdoor brand that offers signature outerwear; men's and women's clothing, gear and accessories; and world-class mountaineering gear. All built to one standard—to be the best.

OUR CREED
To give you such outstanding quality, value, service and guarantee that we may be worthy of your high esteem.™

OUR GUARANTEE
Every item we sell will give you complete satisfaction or you may return it for a full refund.™
